<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta content='text/html; charset=UTF-8' http-equiv='Content-Type' />
  </head>
  <body>
    <h1><%= @user.name %></h1>
    <p>
      	Your application for <%= @clan.name %> has been created. <br/>
      	If your application is accepted you will be contacted in game, otherwise you will receive a rejection email. <br />
      	If you are currently in a clan, please do not leave that clan until contacted and instructed to.      
    </p>
    <p>
    	If you don't already have teamspeak, please download and install it. <br/>
    	<a href="http://www.instantteamspeak.com//teamspeak-download.php" target='_blank'> TeamSpeak Download </a> <br/>
    	Even if you don't have a microphone teamspeak will be valuable in coorinating battles.<br/>
    </p>
    <p>	
    	The Clan TeamSpeak Server Address: <%= CLAN_TEAMSPEAK_SERVER %> <br/ >
		Password: <%= CLAN_TEAMSPEAK_PASSWORD %><br />
    </p>
    <p>
      	Login to the site to check if you've been accepted to <%= @clan.name %> using this link: <%= link_to @user.name, @url %> 
    </p>
    <p>
    	Certain areas of <%= @clan.name %>'s site might not be accessible to members that are not official in the clan.    	
    </p>
  </body>
</html>